[Over the past 2 weeks, Haiti has experienced 2650 more cases of cholera with 22 more deaths. Although no additional cases have been reported from Cuba, nongovernmental sources have continued to report new cases. - Mod.LL

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/22DW.]
